Package: robustrolling
Type: Package
Title: Rolling Window Metrics via C++17
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Igor", "Ptak",
    email = "ptakigor2005@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: High-performance rolling window metrics implemented in C++17.
    Provides numerically stable, O(1) algorithms for variance, mean, skewness,
    kurtosis, covariance, Pearson correlation, maximum, minimum, and median,
    with full NA handling and min_periods semantics compatible with pandas.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: C++17
NeedsCompilation: yes
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Suggests: tinytest
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
